{% style %}#shopify-section-{{ section.id }}{background:{{ section.settings.bg }};color:{{ section.settings.text }};padding-top:{{ section.settings.padding_top }}px;padding-bottom:{{ section.settings.padding_bottom }}px}{% endstyle %}
{% if section.settings.custom_html != blank %}
  {{ section.settings.custom_html }}
{% else %}
{% if section.settings.custom_svg != blank %}<div class="se-custom-svg">{{ section.settings.custom_svg }}</div>{% endif %}
        <section class="founder-story__moment-harbor-ripple">
            <div class="water-science__fact-crest-pulse">
                <div class="reveal-up hero__panel-bloom-ember">
                    <div class="concern-section__point-bloom-zenith">
                        <div class="founder-story__moment-harbor-solace">👩&zwj;⚕️</div>
                        <div class="section-eyebrow concern-section__point-crest-bloom">THE WOMAN BEHIND SHOWERENVY</div>
                        <h2 class="water-science__fact-crest-thrive">She Didn't Set Out to Build a Product.<br><span class="water-science__fact-crest-uplift">She Set Out to Solve Her Own Problem.</span></h2></div>
                </div>
                <div class="founder-story__moment-harbor-thrive">
                    <div class="reveal-left hero__panel-bloom-ember">
                        <div>
                            <div class="founder-story__moment-harbor-uplift">
                                <div class="founder-story__moment-harbor-velvet"><span class="hero__panel-aurora-oasis">👩&zwj;⚕️</span><span class="trust-strip__signal-bloom-thrive">Dr. Emily Hart — Founder Portrait</span><span class="trust-strip__signal-bloom-uplift">Upload image here</span></div>
                            </div>
                            <div class="founder-story__moment-harbor-whisper">
                                <div class="founder-story__moment-harbor-xenial">Dr. Emily Hart, MD</div>
                                <div class="founder-story__moment-harbor-yonder">Dermatologist · Water Quality Researcher</div>
                                <div class="founder-story__moment-harbor-zenith">Board-Certified, 22+ Years in Practice</div>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                    <div class="reveal-right hero__panel-bloom-ember">
                        <div>
                            <p class="founder-story__moment-ivory-aurora">For two decades, Dr. Emily Hart treated women over 45 for the same frustrating pattern: chronic dry skin, thinning hair, and treatments that never seemed to hold. She prescribed the best dermatological products available. They
                                helped — but never fully.</p>
                            <p class="founder-story__moment-ivory-aurora">Then, at 52, it happened to her. The same crepe-like skin. The same hair in the drain. The same serums that worked at 40 suddenly failing. As a dermatologist, she knew the biology — estrogen decline reduces collagen by 30%
                                in the first five years of menopause. But something else was accelerating the damage.</p>
                            <div class="founder-story__moment-ivory-bloom">
                                <p class="founder-story__moment-ivory-crest">"I tested my shower water on a whim. What came back stunned me — chlorine levels high enough to damage keratin bonds, calcium deposits that physically block product absorption, and trace heavy metals I'd never want near
                                    my patients' skin."</p>
                                <p class="founder-story__moment-ivory-drift">— Dr. Emily Hart</p>
                            </div>
                            <p class="founder-story__moment-ivory-aurora">She realized something that changed everything: she had spent 22 years treating symptoms while her patients went home and showered in the cause. Every morning, untreated water stripped the natural oils their bodies were already
                                struggling to produce. Every serum she prescribed was fighting water chemistry it could never overcome.</p>
                            <p class="founder-story__moment-ivory-aurora">Existing shower filters removed chlorine — partially. None addressed the full spectrum: chloramines, heavy metals, VOCs, hard water minerals. And none replaced what menopausal skin actually needs. So she built one that does
                                both.</p>
                            <p class="founder-story__moment-ivory-ember">ShowerEnvy's 15-stage filtration was designed by a doctor who knows what a woman's body loses after 45 — and what her water should put back. Vitamin A to support collagen production. Vitamin C to neutralize chlorine and protect
                                against oxidative stress. Vitamin E to rebuild the moisture barrier her hormones can no longer maintain alone.</p>
                            <div class="content-layout founder-story__moment-ivory-flare">
                                <div class="card founder-story__moment-ivory-glow"><span class="founder-story__moment-ivory-harbor">🎓</span><span class="founder-story__moment-ivory-ivory">MD from Johns Hopkins School of Medicine</span></div>
                                <div class="card founder-story__moment-ivory-jade"><span class="founder-story__moment-ivory-harbor">🏥</span><span class="founder-story__moment-ivory-ivory">22 years in clinical dermatology practice</span></div>
                                <div class="card founder-story__moment-ivory-kindle"><span class="founder-story__moment-ivory-harbor">📋</span><span class="founder-story__moment-ivory-ivory">Published researcher on water quality &amp; skin health</span></div>
                                <div class="card founder-story__moment-ivory-glow"><span class="founder-story__moment-ivory-harbor">👩&zwj;👩&zwj;👧</span><span class="founder-story__moment-ivory-ivory">Created ShowerEnvy after experiencing menopause firsthand</span></div>
                            </div>
                            <div class="founder-story__moment-ivory-lumen">
                                <p class="founder-story__moment-ivory-meadow">"I didn't create ShowerEnvy to sell showerheads. I created it because I was tired of watching women spend thousands on products that can't work — while the real problem runs through their pipes every morning."</p>
                                <div class="founder-story__moment-ivory-nova">
                                    <div class="founder-story__moment-ivory-oasis">EH</div>
                                    <div>
                                        <div class="founder-story__moment-ivory-pulse">Dr. Emily Hart, MD</div>
                                        <div class="founder-story__moment-ivory-quartz">Founder, ShowerEnvy</div>
                                    </div>
                                </div>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </section>

{% endif %}
{% schema %}
{
  "name":"SE Founder",
  "settings":[
    {"type":"color","id":"bg","label":"Background color","default":"#ffffff"},
    {"type":"color","id":"text","label":"Text color","default":"#1f1d1a"},
    {"type":"range","id":"padding_top","label":"Padding top","min":0,"max":120,"step":4,"unit":"px","default":0},
    {"type":"range","id":"padding_bottom","label":"Padding bottom","min":0,"max":120,"step":4,"unit":"px","default":0},
    {"type":"image_picker","id":"section_image","label":"Section image (optional)"},
    {"type":"image_picker","id":"section_image_mobile","label":"Section image mobile (optional)"}
    ,{"type":"liquid","id":"custom_html","label":"Custom section HTML (advanced)"}
    ,{"type":"liquid","id":"custom_svg","label":"Custom SVG/HTML snippet (advanced)"}
  ],
  "presets":[{"name":"SE Founder"}]
}
{% endschema %}
